"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1938572-Olympics-Matt-Richardson-Team-GB-ban\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Matthew Richardson could be handed a two-year ban from cycling following his shock defection toTeam GB.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 20, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Richardson_(footballer)\", \"score\": 0.9918787924836031, \"rank\": 0.007602339181287399, \"text\": \"Matthew Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Richardson_(footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Richardson_(footballer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cyclist, who took three medals at the recent Paris Games for Australia,announced his attention to switch allegiances earlier this week.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9994323751700471, \"rank\": 0.00040425960233436714, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes just days after he made theOlympicpodium in the French capital on three occasions, with cycling chiefs at AusCycling reported to have been left stunned by the decision.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 305, \"end\": 311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9938895016881325, \"rank\": 0.005913314619429663, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AusCycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So much so, that the Australian officials could explore a clause that would see Richardson banned from competing for Team GB until 2026.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.8247313871947568, \"rank\": 0.14279521381346952, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999984006566649, \"rank\": 1.5993458422597712e-06, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after the defection, AusCycling's executive general manager, Jesse Korf said: \\\"There is disappointment around the decision and the process and not knowing around Matt's circumstances.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For sure he will not compete at the upcoming world championships [in October].\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the non-competition duration and clauses, that is being interrogated and looked into at the moment together with the UCI and ASC (Australian Sports Commission).\\\"\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.999991790625518, \"rank\": 7.724322530547494e-06, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\", \"score\": 0.9660423223826007, \"rank\": 0.022409149221099822, \"text\": \"ASC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\"}, {\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Sports Commission\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"That is something that we would have to discuss internally because we obviously have a big say in that and we need to review that\\u2026    \\\"So that would have to be a conversation to get to a joint decision [with the stakeholders] before we can share that and start a conversation with UCI and Matt and British Cycling.\\\"\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.999991790625518, \"rank\": 7.724322530547494e-06, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson was British-born but had moved to Australia at an early age and has competed under the Australian flag ever since breaking into the sport.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999984006566649, \"rank\": 1.5993458422597712e-06, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9994323751700471, \"rank\": 0.00040425960233436714, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He finished the Games as Australia's most successful cyclist in Paris, but has cited a 'childhood dream' of competing for Team GB as the reason for his shock switch.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1516, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9994323751700471, \"rank\": 0.00040425960233436714, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996990277848, \"rank\": 3.0097235368434893e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OnInstagram, the newest member of Team GB's cycling team said: \\\"I have made the decision to pack up my entire life and move half way across the world to begin the next chapter in my cycling career.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6950377531958732, \"rank\": 0.32496847087198294, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is with a sense of excitement and renewal I announce I have joined the Great British Cycling Team.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1936, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Switching nationality was a difficult decision, and not one I took lightly.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a personal choice, made after careful consideration of my career and future.\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not something I decided on quickly or easily\\u2026  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"But this decision is about following my passion and pushing myself to new heights.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not about leaving something behind, but about embracing a new chapter in my journey and chasing a dream, a dream that is to race for the country in which I was born.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope you can understand and support me as I continue to give my best in the sport I love.\\\"\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.951168552699141e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2958, \"end\": 2971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.951168552699141e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"